HEADWORD: Paddlewood
<hw>Pad"dle*wood`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>The light elastic wood of the <spn>Aspidosperma excelsum</spn>, a
tree of Guiana having a fluted trunk readily split into
planks.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

